STATE of North Carolina
v.
Lorenzo DUARTE. No. 653P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 19, 2006. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Jeff Hunt, District Attorney, for State. William D. Auman, for Duarte.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Attorney General on the 23rd day of November 2005 for Writ of Supersedeas of the judgment of the Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 19th day of December 2006."
